    </h1><p></p><p class="font_8" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; pointer-events: auto; line-height: normal; letter-spacing: normal;"><span style="font-family: din-next-w01-light, din-next-w02-light, din-next-w10-light, sans-serif;">„</span>Logopedas patarė su vaiku šnekėti tik angliškai<span style="font-family: din-next-w01-light, din-next-w02-light, din-next-w10-light, sans-serif;">“</span>&nbsp;<span style="font-family: din-next-w01-light, din-next-w02-light, din-next-w10-light, sans-serif;">—&nbsp;</span>tokiomis problemomis dalinasi Pasakos tėvai ir globėjai.</p>
    <p class="font_8" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; pointer-events: auto; line-height: normal; letter-spacing: normal;">
        &nbsp;</p><p class="font_8" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; pointer-events: auto; line-height: normal; letter-spacing: normal;">
        Nesijaudinkite, jūsų vaikas tikrai puikiai šnekės angliškai (ar kita jūsų aplinkoje vartojama kalba). Logopedai,
        išmanantys vaiko kalbos raidą, tikrai tokių patarimų neturėtų duoti.</p><p class="font_8" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; pointer-events: auto; line-height: normal; letter-spacing: normal;">
        Dvikalbėse arba daugiakalbėse situacijose dažniausiai lietuvių kalba yra mažumos kalba (ja kalba tik vaiko tėvai
        arba vienas iš tėvų). Tokioje situacijoje anglų ar kitos kalbos dažniausiai būna dominuojančios kalbos (ją
        vaikas girdi už namų ribų: darželyje, mokykloje, tarp draugų, parduotuvėje). Dominuojančią kalbą vaikas puikiai
        įsisavins net jei ją aktyviai pradės vartoti ir vėliau, pavyzdžiui, kai eis į darželį ar mokyklą. Vaikai puikiai
        sugeba įsisavinti kelias kalbas vienu metu. Deja, dominuojanti kalba, ypač mokyklinukų atveju, palaipsniui
        užgožia lietuvių kalbą. Tad labai svarbu jau nuo pat kūdikystės šnekėti su vaiku tik lietuviškai ir stengtis to
        susitarimo šeimoje laikytis.</p><p></p><h1></h1><h1 class="font_0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; pointer-events: auto; font-size: 25px; line-height: normal;">
        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 34px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: playfairdisplay-bold, &quot;playfair display&quot;, serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(84, 239, 209);">+&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">Su vaiku kalbu lietuviškai, bet jis vis tiek su manimi kalba angliškai, ką daryti?</span>
    </h1><p></p><p class="font_8" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; pointer-events: auto; line-height: normal; letter-spacing: normal;">
        Dažnai tėvai kreipiasi į mus šiuo klausimu. Dalinamės keliais patarimais. Jei vaikas jums sako:&nbsp;<span style="font-family: din-next-w01-light, din-next-w02-light, din-next-w10-light, sans-serif;">„</span>Mommy water!<span style="font-family: din-next-w01-light, din-next-w02-light, din-next-w10-light, sans-serif;">“</span>&nbsp;Tokiu atveju:</p><p class="font_8" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; pointer-events: auto; line-height: normal; letter-spacing: normal;">
        - tęskite vaiko pradėtą dialogą gimtąja kalba:&nbsp;<span style="font-family: din-next-w01-light, din-next-w02-light, din-next-w10-light, sans-serif;">„</span>aha, ir aš esu ištroškusi, einame atsigerti vandens. Į
        kokį puodelį tau įpilti: žalią ar mėlyną?<span style="font-family: din-next-w01-light, din-next-w02-light, din-next-w10-light, sans-serif;">“</span>&nbsp;<span style="font-family: din-next-w01-light, din-next-w02-light, din-next-w10-light, sans-serif;">—</span>&nbsp;tai turėtų paskatinti vaiką atsakyti lietuviškai (nebūtinai iš
        karto);</p><p class="font_8" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; pointer-events: auto; line-height: normal; letter-spacing: normal;">
        - papasakokite vaikui, kaip jūs jaučiatės, kai vaikas kalba lietuviškai:&nbsp;<span style="font-family: din-next-w01-light, din-next-w02-light, din-next-w10-light, sans-serif;">„</span>aš tave geriau suprantu, kai tu kalbi
        lietuviškai<span style="font-family: din-next-w01-light, din-next-w02-light, din-next-w10-light, sans-serif;">“</span>,&nbsp;<span style="font-family: din-next-w01-light, din-next-w02-light, din-next-w10-light, sans-serif;">„</span>man taip gera, kai tu man atsakai lietuviškai<span style="font-family: din-next-w01-light, din-next-w02-light, din-next-w10-light, sans-serif;">“</span>;</p><p class="font_8" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; pointer-events: auto; line-height: normal; letter-spacing: normal;">
        - jei jūsų vaikas vartoja lietuviškus žodžius su klaidomis arba sakiniuose maišo kelias kalbas,
        nepertraukinėkite, netaisykite, nekritikuokite. Geriau tęskite pokalbį stengdamiesi į savo
        atsakymą įtraukti vaiko ištartas frazes be klaidų. Jie mokosi iš jūsų!&nbsp;</p><p class="font_8" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; pointer-events: auto; line-height: normal; letter-spacing: normal;">
        - nebauskite ir nekritikuokite vaiko, jei nekalba su jumis lietuviškai:&nbsp;<span style="font-family: din-next-w01-light, din-next-w02-light, din-next-w10-light, sans-serif;">„</span>koks dar water, vanduo!<span style="font-family: din-next-w01-light, din-next-w02-light, din-next-w10-light, sans-serif;">“</span>,&nbsp;<span style="font-family: din-next-w01-light, din-next-w02-light, din-next-w10-light, sans-serif;">„</span>o ką,
        lietuviškai negali paprašyti?<span style="font-family: din-next-w01-light, din-next-w02-light, din-next-w10-light, sans-serif;">“</span>.</p><p></p>
    <h1>
        <div id="comp-kkpdbgyr" class="_2bafp" data-testid="richTextElement" style="margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; pointer-events: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; position: relative; left: 10px; grid-area: 29 / 1 / 30 / 2; place-self: start; width: 391px; height: auto;  font-size: 10px; font-weight: 400;">
            <h1 class="font_0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; pointer-events: auto; font-size: 25px; line-height: normal; color: rgb(var(--color_15));">
                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 34px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: playfairdisplay-bold, &quot;playfair display&quot;, serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(84, 239, 209);">+&nbsp;</span></span></span>Motyvuokite
                ir džiaukitės kartu</h1>
            <div><br></div>
        </div>
        <div id="comp-kkpdbgz2" class="_2bafp" data-testid="richTextElement" style="margin: 0px 0px 37px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; pointer-events: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; position: relative; left: 10px; grid-area: 30 / 1 / 31 / 2; place-self: start; width: 805px; height: auto;  font-size: 10px; font-weight: 400;"></div>
    </h1><p><span style="   letter-spacing: normal;">Labai svarbu, kad vaikas džiaugtųsi kiekvienu, net ir mažu, savo&nbsp;<span style="font-family: din-next-w01-light, din-next-w02-light, din-next-w10-light, sans-serif;">„</span>laimėjimu<span style="font-family: din-next-w01-light, din-next-w02-light, din-next-w10-light, sans-serif;">“</span>. Pagirkite ir kartu&nbsp;švęskite dėl<span style="font-family: din-next-w01-light, din-next-w02-light, din-next-w10-light, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span>naujų išmoktų žodžių arba perskaitytos lietuviškos knygos. Išduosim paslaptį&nbsp;<span style="font-family: din-next-w01-light, din-next-w02-light, din-next-w10-light, sans-serif;">—&nbsp;</span>lipdukai kartais daro stebuklus!&nbsp;</span>
    </p><h1></h1><h1 class="font_0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; pointer-events: auto; font-size: 25px; line-height: normal;">
        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 34px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: playfairdisplay-bold, &quot;playfair display&quot;, serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(84, 239, 209);">+&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">Kaip paskatinti vaiką daugiau kalbėti lietuviškai?</span>
    </h1><p></p><p class="font_8" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; pointer-events: auto; line-height: normal; letter-spacing: normal;">
        Kuo daugiau vaikas girdi lietuvių kalbą, tuo didesnė tikimybė, kad jis pradės geriau kalbėti lietuviškai. Visgi
        neužtenka tik girdėti&nbsp;<span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">–</span>&nbsp;vaikai geriausiai mokosi kalbų per bendravimą. Mūsų patarimai:</p><p class="font_8" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; pointer-events: auto; line-height: normal; letter-spacing: normal;">
        Kai skaitote lietuvišką knygą vaikams, bendraukite ir įtraukite juos į pasakojimą:&nbsp;<span style="font-family: din-next-w01-light, din-next-w02-light, din-next-w10-light, sans-serif;">„</span>kokius piešinėlius matai? Ką
        čia daro karvė? O kaip manai, ką dabar pasakys lapiukas?<span style="font-family: din-next-w01-light, din-next-w02-light, din-next-w10-light, sans-serif;">“</span></p><p class="font_8" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; pointer-events: auto; line-height: normal; letter-spacing: normal;">
        Kai gaminate pusryčius, pasikvieskite vaikus į pagalbą! Kalbėkite, ką darote, kokius maisto produktus
        naudojate.</p><p class="font_8" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; pointer-events: auto; line-height: normal; letter-spacing: normal;">
        Kai žiūrite lietuviškus filmukus, žiūrėkite kartu ir aptarkite herojų veiksmus, išvaizdą, siužetą.</p><p></p><h1 style="text-align: center; color:#54efd1"> Sėkmės!</h1>                        @endsection